jnxJsDns.name: jnxJsDns
jnxJsDns.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net
jnxJsDns.description: This MIB provides collated statistics for the Domain Name System (DNS) proxy collected over all interfaces on which it is configured to serve

jnxJsDNSProxyQueriesReceived.name: jnxJsDNSProxyQueriesReceived
jnxJsDNSProxyQueriesReceived.description: Count of total number of DNS queries received by the DNS Proxy.

jnxJsDnsProxyResponsesSent.name: jnxJsDnsProxyResponsesSent
jnxJsDnsProxyResponsesSent.description: Count of DNS queries answered sent by the DNS Proxy. This includes DNS cache hits and misses that were answered.

jnxJsDnsProxyQueriesForwarded.name: jnxJsDnsProxyQueriesForwarded
jnxJsDnsProxyQueriesForwarded.description: Count of DNS queries forwarded to other DNS server. This is number of queries that have been proxied due to cache miss.

jnxJsDnsProxyNegativeResponses.name: jnxJsDnsProxyNegativeResponses
jnxJsDnsProxyNegativeResponses.description: Count of Negative DNS query responses. This is the count of DNS queries that the Proxy could not obtain answers for.

jnxJsDnsProxyRetryRequests.name: jnxJsDnsProxyRetryRequests
jnxJsDnsProxyRetryRequests.description: Count of DNS retry queries that this proxy received.

jnxJsDnsProxyPendingRequests.name: jnxJsDnsProxyPendingRequests
jnxJsDnsProxyPendingRequests.description: Count of DNS requests yet to be answered.
